        public void setLightType(java.lang.String lightType)
        Set the type of the light depending on a String representation retrieved from the bridge. When light type is an unknown type, the light will default to a ON_OFF_LIGHT. When light type is null, the light will default to a CT_COLOR_LIGHT.
        Parameters:
        lightType - the new light type.
